         <abstract id="aspace_cb96871ca2033833368bcab7e4e89ee1">Personal papers and research notes of Norton Canfield relating to audiology. Included are papers documenting a national hearing survey, a Connecticut hearing survey, various New Haven, Connecticut projects, and an Army hearing center.</abstract>
